The paper deals with the problem of phase retrieval, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and computer vision (cs.CV). The PhaseLift method, which is the focus of the paper, is a technique used in machine learning (cs.LG) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). The paper also discusses the properties of subgaussian measurements, which is a topic in signal processing (cs.SI).
